        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Can I see a sample before buying?</summary>
          <p>Yes &mdash; download the <a href="/free-sample/">free sample kit</a> first, no email or signup required. It includes a real Risk Assessment and COSHH Assessment from our Cleaning Business Kit.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Get Compliant Today</h2>
      <p>Choose your trade-specific H&amp;S kit and be audit-ready in 60 minutes. One-time purchase. Yours forever.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/kits/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">View All Kits &mdash; From &pound;49</a>
        <a href="/free-sample/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Try Free Sample</a>
      </div>
